├── github_workflows/          ✅ Underscores, lowercase
├── test_fixtures/             ✅ Underscores, lowercase
├── api_documentation/         ✅ Underscores, lowercase
├── utility_scripts/           ✅ Underscores, lowercase
└── code_review_templates/     ✅ Multiple underscores, lowercase
` ``

### ❌ Incorrect Directory Names

` ``text
stdlib/
├── cursor-rules/              ❌ Dashes (should use underscores)
├── githubWorkflows/           ❌ CamelCase (should be github_workflows)
├── test fixtures/             ❌ Space (should be test_fixtures)
├── API_Documentation/         ❌ Capitalization (should be api_documentation)
├── utility-scripts/           ❌ Dashes (should be utility_scripts)
