` ``

### Common Violations and Fixes

**Dash Usage (Wrong Separator):**
` ``text
❌ cursor-rules/           →  ✅ cursor_rules/
❌ github-workflows/       →  ✅ github_workflows/
❌ test-fixtures/          →  ✅ test_fixtures/
❌ api-docs/               →  ✅ api_docs/
` ``

**CamelCase Violations:**
` ``text
❌ testFixtures/           →  ✅ test_fixtures/
❌ apiDocumentation/       →  ✅ api_documentation/
❌ utilityScripts/         →  ✅ utility_scripts/
❌ githubWorkflows/        →  ✅ github_workflows/
` ``

**Space and Capitalization:**
` ``text
❌ API Docs/               →  ✅ api_docs/
❌ Test Fixtures/          →  ✅ test_fixtures/
❌ Utility Scripts/        →  ✅ utility_scripts/
❌ Code Review/            →  ✅ code_review/
` ``

### Validation Commands

**Find Non-Compliant Directories:**
` ``bash
# Find directories with dashes
find . -type d -name "*-*" | grep -v ".git"

# Find directories with uppercase
find . -type d | grep -E "[A-Z]"

# Find directories with spaces
find . -type d -name "* *"
` ``

**Batch Rename Non-Compliant Directories:**
` ``bash
# Convert dashes to underscores
for dir in $(find . -type d -name "*-*" | grep -v ".git"); do
  newname=$(echo "$dir" | sed 's/-/_/g')
  mv "$dir" "$newname"
done

# Convert to lowercase
for dir in $(find . -type d | grep -E "[A-Z]"); do
  newname=$(echo "$dir" | tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]')
  mv "$dir" "$newname"
done
` ``

